casebody.data:
A./S. IVARANS REDERI (Ivan An. Christensen, Manager) OF OSLO, NORWAY, Sole Owner and Claimant of THE S. S. MODEMI, et al., Appellants, v. WILLIAM WRIGLEY, JR., COMPANY, et al., Appellees. No. 6515. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. July 20, 1932.

Before BRYAN, SIBLEY, and, HUTCHESON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The petition for rehearing in the above numbered and entitled cause is denied.
